{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_01HRSQ6kAeFN6hrvNRCrTp36","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The new `population.go` adds a population management system under `.cloche/evolution/population/<step-name>/`. Let me check if the self-evolution design doc's \"On-Disk Evolution State\" section needs updating, and if the CLAUDE.md project layout needs updating.\n\nThe self-evolution design doc at line 145-153 shows:\n```\n.cloche/\n  evolution/\n    log.jsonl\n    knowledge/\n      develop.md\n    snapshots/\n      <timestamp>-<filename>\n```\n\nThis doesn't include the new `population/` directory. Let me also check if there's anything in CLAUDE.md or other docs that should reference this.\n\n\nCLAUDE.md focuses on the user-facing project layout and doesn't document the `.cloche/` evolution structure at all, so I need to update the self-evolution design doc to include the population directory structure.","signature":""}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":7611,"cache_read_input_tokens":24657,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":7611},"output_tokens":8,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"b01b4e7c-06dd-40f1-863a-61952eecce5b","uuid":"bea93a64-e031-4a35-88f8-451cc5ffe76e"}
